```css
/* Variables */
:root {
  --accordion-width: 400px;
  --accordion-color: #333;
  --accordion-hover-bg: rgba(40, 120, 145, 0.05);
  --icon-size: 12px;
  --icon-line-width: 2px;
  --transition-speed: 0.3s;
  --font-family: "Roboto", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

/* Base Accordion Styles */
.accordion {
  width: var(--accordion-width);
  max-width: 100%;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* Header Styles */
.accordion summary.accordion-header {
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: var(--font-family);
  border: none;
  background: none;
  padding: 0;
  transition: background-color var(--transition-speed);
}

/* Size Variants */
.accordion.default .accordion-header {
  padding: var(--padding-default);
  font-size: var(--font-size-default);
}

.accordion.compact .accordion-header {
  padding: var(--padding-compact);
  font-size: var(--font-size-compact);
}

.accordion.compact .accordion-body {
  padding: 0 12px 12px;
}

/* Title Styles */
.accordion-title {
  font-weight: bold;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accordion-color);
}

/* Icon Styles */
.accordion-icon {
  width: var(--icon-size);
  height: var(--icon-size);
  position: relative;
  transition: transform var(--transition-speed) ease;
}

.accordion-icon::before,
.accordion-icon::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  background-color: var(--accordion-color);
  transition: transform var(--transition-speed) ease;
}

.accordion-icon::before {
  width: var(--icon-line-width);
  height: 100%;
  left: 50%;
  top: 0;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}

.accordion-icon::after {
  height: var(--icon-line-width);
  width: 100%;
  top: 50%;
  left: 0;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
}

.accordion[open] .accordion-icon::before {
  transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(90deg);
  transform-origin: center;
}

/* Content Styles */
.accordion-content {
  max-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: max-height var(--transition-speed) ease-out;
  font-family: var(--font-family);
  font-weight: normal;
}

.accordion-content.open {
  max-height: 500px;
}

.accordion-body {
  padding: 0 20px 20px;
  font-family: var(--font-family);
  font-weight: normal;
}

/* Interactive States */
.accordion-header:hover {
  background-color: var(--accordion-hover-bg);
}

/* Remove default summary styles */
.accordion > summary {
  list-style: none;
}

.accordion > summary::-webkit-details-marker {
  display: none;
}
```

Key improvements made:

1. Added CSS variables for commonly used values
2. Organized code into logical sections with comments
3. Consolidated repeated properties (like font-family)
4. Made transitions consistent using variables
5. Grouped related styles together
6. Made colors and dimensions more maintainable through variables
7. Improved readability with consistent spacing and organization

